Class Property

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.hsb.ms.syn.common.audio.Property
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Property
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Data structure for one property of a DraggableNode's AudioAlgorithm. This is a basic structure holding three floating-points and a String name that may be used to describe a UI Slider that may alter its value, for instance
